&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leverage Ecosystem:&lt;/strong&gt; Tap into Bay Area’s &lt;strong&gt;PE, VC, and professional services networks&lt;/strong&gt; to source opportunities and accelerate pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
